The CO (1-0) line is redshifted to 115.06 GHz, where we will center the main baseband with a bandwidth of 1221 km/s and with 0.6 km/s resolution. Two basebands (2 and 4) are set to TDM. Baseband 3 is set to the low-resolution FDM and covers the H2CO line, but can be used for continuum as well.</prj:justificationText>
